44:49.270 --> 44:51.306
We are in a world of fucked up, Jess.

44:53.524 --> 44:55.936
I mean, I'm gonna lose my best friend.

44:56.777 --> 44:59.154
Don't tell me about loss.

45:01.449 --> 45:02.905
Uh....

45:03.075 --> 45:07.785
Even without your blood in me,
you are all I think about.

45:11.667 --> 45:14.158
What the hell am I supposed to do now?

45:15.796 --> 45:16.831
Wish I knew.

45:27.183 --> 45:31.301
You know, after all the freaky shit
I've been seeing...

45:31.479 --> 45:34.391
...some shit don't seem so freaky
to me no more.

45:34.565 --> 45:36.897
But tonight? Mm.

45:38.694 --> 45:40.309
That was some freaky shit.

45:43.491 --> 45:47.029
-Can't believe Marnie's gone.
-You ain't blaming yourself, is you?

45:49.956 --> 45:51.992
-I don't know.
-No.

45:52.166 --> 45:54.407
No,no,no.

45:54.585 --> 45:55.916
Marnie was a big girl.

45:56.087 --> 45:58.999
She made up her own motherfucking mind
to hold folks hostage...

45:59.173 --> 46:00.379
...and murder her friends.

46:00.549 --> 46:03.757
Ain't no way that bad juju
wasn't gonna come back to her.

46:05.012 --> 46:09.051
-That's true.
-Truer than rain, lover.

46:09.225 --> 46:12.592
You galloped in and saved some folks
tonight.

46:12.770 --> 46:14.761
Never fucking forget that.

46:17.608 --> 46:19.018
I know.

46:22.863 --> 46:25.855
We're alive and we're safe.

46:26.033 --> 46:27.773
Be happy for that.

46:30.913 --> 46:32.494
lam.

46:44.593 --> 46:46.003
[SIGHS]

